        "Description": "Good evening, Agent 47.\r\rNew intelligence reveals Emma Carlsie acted under orders. The source remains unknown, but we’ve identified a key intermediary: Neha, a gang leader based in Mumbai.\r\rYour objectives are clear. Eliminate Neha and retrieve her phone. Additionally, deal with her two bodyguards, Vivek Saral and Amarjeet Vimal, as they may hold critical links to the client.\r\rAll targets are located within a tightly controlled residential area.\r\rFurther instructions will follow.\r\rGood luck, 47",
